  storyboardSlides:
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: ad181ad04595d38beb157740006aa831, type: 3}
    titleText: Brother Against Brother
    bodyText: In the heart of the colony, Astrid confronts his mutated brother Sydnell,
      now a boss with regenerative health and aggressive charges. Rex intervenes,
      raging at the intrusion and commanding Sydnell to eliminate the threat.
  winStoryboardSlides:
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: afa5422131651804c9101cef2e20d38b, type: 3}
    titleText: Redemption and Restoration
    bodyText: Astrid Starhall defeated Rex Thalor and deactivated the nuclear threat,
      and all entities including his rescued brother returned to their normal forms.
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 59c6ef887528582cab6beb43d1884c46, type: 3}
    titleText: Hero of Namek
    bodyText: "Word of Astrid\u2019s victory spreads across the galaxy. The Stellar
      Galactic Authority, once silent, can no longer ignore his defiance and success. "
  instructionPanel: {fileID: 432419544}
  instructionSlides:
  - image: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 86bbe6fdbc4ce5177bf3c860687a2ae3, type: 3}
    bodyText: "Defeat Sydnell Starhorld\n\nYour brother Sydnell has been corrupted
      by the AI Core. He now guards the Reactor Chamber as its final line of defense.
      Sydnell is powerful \u2014 he will charge, leap, and self-heal in his second
      phase.\nAt 50% health he will call reinforcements and become more aggressive.\n\nPut
      him down to save the colony."
